---
title: Lemon Chicken Noodles  with Roasted Sesame Seeds and Green Beans
description: Perfect for kids and grown-ups alike, these Lemon Chicken Noodles are sure to become a new family favourite. Our easy tips and tweaks will help you create a dish that's to everyone's tastes! For little ones, serve sesame in a bowl for optional sprinkling.
